Description:
This dataset includes:
-recordings of interviews with 24 people on the topic of climate change, carbon capture and storage and social transitions in Tomakomai, Hokkaido and Japan more widely (in Japanese);
-notes from historical environmental impact assessments, news stories and policy documents pertaining to industrial development in Tomakomai, collected from Tomakomai City Library and Hokkaido Library;
-field notes and photographs taken by Dr Mabon during his field research in Tomakomai/Hokkaido from May-June 2016.
